{"tid":284283,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"召集連登所有獸醫護士","createTime":"2017-06-14T19:21:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T14:00:32.000Z","uid":65690,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"09ad19f22b246502d67aafd396af56f75304a2fc","tid":284283,"uid":65690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T19:21:42.000Z","msg":"究竟呢行有無前景? 頂薪係咪真係google講既20k? 之後進修有無得加?<br />\n<br />\n自問真係愛動物，但人工似乎真係太低，計返時薪得個$50零蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而且工時長!<br />\n<br />\n今年文科u grad，猶豫緊要唔要入行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1428f7f2b4ee14c79d25f9e790a698af2dce1213","tid":284283,"uid":47996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T19:32:12.000Z","msg":"想做就做啦 最緊要係你嘅夢想"},{"pid":"dbb150caa841ddc39b7b2c94d04005709fa413ad","tid":284283,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T19:34:03.000Z","msg":"中六畢業<br />\n唔識英文普通話<br />\n請唔請？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"614df703ce800d8e60f832edc642c28715a595d4","tid":284283,"uid":112184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T19:53:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>究竟呢行有無前景? 頂薪係咪真係google講既20k? 之後進修有無得加?<br />\n<br />\n自問真係愛動物，但人工似乎真係太低，計返時薪得個$50零蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而且工時長!<br />\n<br />\n今年文科u grad，猶豫緊要唔要入行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係，進修同年資都係加薪因素，不過要有30K 好難。<br />\n無經驗入行同做奴工無分別。"},{"pid":"d8f78511e00031fc6ed253b64d3b1c508a900dd3","tid":284283,"uid":118776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T19:53:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9ab4e3a24d2cb513b0363b8e7e5181b2dd9e175","tid":284283,"uid":118776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T19:54:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中六畢業<br />\n唔識英文普通話<br />\n請唔請？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n細診所你見工果時正正常常 都會請"},{"pid":"21e32ee7c85e80a156d0a6e4032ce913ec1a9fc0","tid":284283,"uid":112184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T19:55:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中六畢業<br />\n唔識英文普通話<br />\n請唔請？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔識普通話基本上唔大問題，唔識英文可以搵嘅診所選擇會少好多。"},{"pid":"43dbabcf22467401e27210630a7d89e98fb7af33","tid":284283,"uid":118776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T19:57:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55da723b61add4764e664b781da0ccb2696010f0","tid":284283,"uid":112184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T19:57:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n絲打你係捱夜姑娘？"},{"pid":"1cff8a845e2d7aa162b7ee7ec74fc9a5422885e4","tid":284283,"uid":118776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T19:58:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n絲打你係捱夜姑娘？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未做過夜更<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a638227a3781da7157881e39bf41737a2207764","tid":284283,"uid":112184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T19:58:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n絲打你係捱夜姑娘？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未做過夜更<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n做咩咁夜都唔瞓咁睇唔開"},{"pid":"464b0ffcf6057f4809b69ff3d3750b417387a8d9","tid":284283,"uid":110362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T20:00:11.000Z","msg":"我都想入行但u讀econ會唔會唔請？ 其實我都係好熱愛動物 想做啲關動物嘅工作但唔知有咩選擇 因為完全無任何bio/chem底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d41aaf83e9bdc837fcd101345adaa750e7010e6","tid":284283,"uid":112184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T20:00:35.000Z","msg":"真心屎尿蟲血都唔係最難頂，老屎忽先係最最最難頂！"},{"pid":"46cba3dfa23393a9e555c71a5e5121250262f995","tid":284283,"uid":118776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T20:01:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n絲打你係捱夜姑娘？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未做過夜更<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n做咩咁夜都唔瞓咁睇唔開</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nQuit左 而家唔洗做好得閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a74829be6bed1a0cb5f6fa6a6b798cd7b9f852b","tid":284283,"uid":112207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T20:01:49.000Z","msg":"唔好入行 只論人工既話我做醫生都做到想轉行<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2039c7c0efb43d2e18731d8f25c16bbd8a7ead47","tid":284283,"uid":118776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T20:02:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真心屎尿蟲血都唔係最難頂，老屎忽先係最最最難頂！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nagger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n岩入行果時俾老屎忽恰<br />\n所以到我做老屎忽果時 我對d新人好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b23e807e24d7dff17624ea30f1b9a4b20e6c8255","tid":284283,"uid":112184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T20:03:03.000Z","msg":"獸醫行業係自殺率最高嘅行業之一。"},{"pid":"fc4a0eec1e86ba0544498b9525a1205e7bb1822a","tid":284283,"uid":118776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T20:04:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想入行但u讀econ會唔會唔請？ 其實我都係好熱愛動物 想做啲關動物嘅工作但唔知有咩選擇 因為完全無任何bio/chem底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多診所都係請f.5 / dse <br />\n其實你唔係7下7下 正正常常有禮貌 就得<br />\n好多姑娘都係冇學歷 冇bio/chem<br />\n<br />\n有養動物係bonus<br />\n英文叻就緊加好 上手會快d"},{"pid":"085d0d030d4469174565caa29b2569ebb3864b1d","tid":284283,"uid":112184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T20:09:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想入行但u讀econ會唔會唔請？ 其實我都係好熱愛動物 想做啲關動物嘅工作但唔知有咩選擇 因為完全無任何bio/chem底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無bio/Chem底上手會難啲。睇你勤唔勤力囉。<br />\n同樓上講一樣，好多中五/DSE畢業都請，不過u grad 識英文一定有著數啲。<br />\n都最後都係睇你個人係點，正正常常唔嫌人工低（真心低）都多數請。"},{"pid":"a581932d333deeae2e25f8343cbddfecaece641d","tid":284283,"uid":112207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T20:09:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想入行但u讀econ會唔會唔請？ 其實我都係好熱愛動物 想做啲關動物嘅工作但唔知有咩選擇 因為完全無任何bio/chem底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你afford 同接受再最低工資加比人撚一年咪可以入行 入行門檻一定唔高"},{"pid":"b6ad79b0de450fa6463c39f51157ccb90dfdf78a","tid":284283,"uid":112184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T20:13:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都想入行但u讀econ會唔會唔請？ 其實我都係好熱愛動物 想做啲關動物嘅工作但唔知有咩選擇 因為完全無任何bio/chem底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你afford 同接受再最低工資加比人撚一年咪可以入行 入行門檻一定唔高</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無上上奴工處睇過？唔明點解出手可以咁低。<br />\n不過嗰啲診所多數都無咩要求。"},{"pid":"ad6b20a8b0d7410d668ded5c04f6cc9bfc321849","tid":284283,"uid":110362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T20:14:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都想入行但u讀econ會唔會唔請？ 其實我都係好熱愛動物 想做啲關動物嘅工作但唔知有咩選擇 因為完全無任何bio/chem底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多診所都係請f.5 / dse <br />\n其實你唔係7下7下 正正常常有禮貌 就得<br />\n好多姑娘都係冇學歷 冇bio/chem<br />\n<br />\n有養動物係bonus<br />\n英文叻就緊加好 上手會快d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁希望英國grad可以幫到我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同想問做完獸醫護士有無機會可以讀啲咩課程考牌成為到獸醫？ 我都唔希望成世淨係做一個獸醫護士 其實定係要重新所有野讀過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5f12e0001d556b3c14934879020355af9d9e82a","tid":284283,"uid":110362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T20:18:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都想入行但u讀econ會唔會唔請？ 其實我都係好熱愛動物 想做啲關動物嘅工作但唔知有咩選擇 因為完全無任何bio/chem底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你afford 同接受再最低工資加比人撚一年咪可以入行 入行門檻一定唔高</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉最擔心唔知點同屋企人交待同左咁多供我讀書最後搵得咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c665bcb471828886156985a3003ca01a1a56f449","tid":284283,"uid":118776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T20:18:32.000Z","msg":"其實呢行流失率好高<br />\n好多人岩岩入行 做幾日，一個禮拜，2個月就頂唔順辭職<br />\n<br />\n岩入行人工低 工時長 ot多 workload重 老屎忽文化嚴重 要夠勤力肯捱 你自己諗啦<br />\n<br />\n除左打針 desex 基本上睇得醫生都係唔舒服 可能會好污糟好臭 好多人以為好似寵物店果d咁cute<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你自己諗啦"},{"pid":"e72462bb354c0f0ebcfd23edd912562a474eb4bc","tid":284283,"uid":118776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T20:20:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我都想入行但u讀econ會唔會唔請？ 其實我都係好熱愛動物 想做啲關動物嘅工作但唔知有咩選擇 因為完全無任何bio/chem底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多診所都係請f.5 / dse <br />\n其實你唔係7下7下 正正常常有禮貌 就得<br />\n好多姑娘都係冇學歷 冇bio/chem<br />\n<br />\n有養動物係bonus<br />\n英文叻就緊加好 上手會快d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁希望英國grad可以幫到我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同想問做完獸醫護士有無機會可以讀啲咩課程考牌成為到獸醫？ 我都唔希望成世淨係做一個獸醫護士 其實定係要重新所有野讀過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係u grad 曾經有個客睇唔起我 用英文鬧我 <br />\n我用英文答返佢 佢即刻冇聲出 有d客會狗眼看人低架<br />\n<br />\n獸醫要讀degree 冇得就咁轉"}]}